data.description: Move in ready! Check out this spacious, 2 story condo with 2 bedrooms, 1.5 baths and a 1 car detached garage. The main level has a half bath and a large kitchen open to the living room that leads to the rear deck overlooking a wooded ravine!! The upper-level features 2 bedrooms, a full bathroom and the lower level includes a finished basement great for entertaining! Refrigerator, range, dishwasher, microwave, washer, and dryer convey with the home! Some of the updates include flooring 2018, furnace/AC 2018, sump pump 2023. HOA fees are $284 a month that includes snow removal, lawn care, exterior building maintenance and trash.
